== Dongy Sela == siwkay niza Dongy Sela (1973.9.19) , wina niza ci Sela, namakay Fongpin Tingalaw a niyazo'. o kawaw niza sa, o mikowanay i Poseko. namicomod to Lobas Mapalaway cacodadad i 2009, katokoh ayza sa, siwa to ko mihcaan. ayzasa amicomod to ko Lomeniay Mapalaway. (amiconos henay to solit.待補充) o sapoyaay a kakoniza o mapalaway a ozip niza namikelih 20170923 lalangawan sapicodadan namikelin 20170924 Palamal milingato a lisin (amiconos henay to solit.待補充) namakayniay a nasolitan nasakamoan ato natinengan Lobas-Mapalaway-aazihen a codad (nay20170924) napatizeng ni Tiway Sayion kalisiw potipot == moazih to tatengaay Holam a komo ==
